items.title: boAt swings back to black in FY25, reports Rs 60 cr PAT ahead of upcoming IPO
items.description: boAt returns to profitability in FY25 with Rs 60 crore PAT, driven by strong audio and wearables growth, premium segment traction, 100+ new product launches, and localisation efforts, setting the stage for its upcoming IPO and continued expansion in domestic and international markets.
